> It got me thinking... If more people drove Volkswagen transporters, 
> they
> probably wouldn't be as stressed out. Simply speaking... you know the 
> Bus
> goes slow as hell, there's nothing you can do about it. So you just 
> learn
> to deal with it, and relax. You know you probably won't make that stop
> light.. so you don't even try. So... you just relax and learn to accept
